      <summary style="cursor:pointer">▶ 如果你想嵌入 YouTube/Bilibili（推荐给大文件）</summary>
      <div style="margin-top:12px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.03); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); border-radius:12px; padding:14px;">
        <p class="desc">把上面的 <code>&lt;video&gt;</code> 替换为下面的 <code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code> 代码即可：</p>
<pre style="overflow:auto; white-space:pre; font-size:13px; padding:12px; background:#0b1220; border-radius:10px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);">
&lt;div class="media"&gt;
  &lt;iframe
    src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/【视频ID】"
    title="YouTube video player"
    frameborder="0"
    allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
    allowfullscreen
    style="width:100%; height:100%"&gt;
  &lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
        <p class="desc">Bilibili 例子（把 av/BV/CID 换成你的）：</p>
<pre style="overflow:auto; white-space:pre; font-size:13px; padding:12px; background:#0b1220; border-radius:10px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);">
&lt;div class="media"&gt;
  &lt;iframe
    src="https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=【BV号】&amp;page=1"
    allowfullscreen
    frameborder="0"
    style="width:100%; height:100%"&gt;
  &lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
      </div>
